    "<p>Architectural historian; one of the first in the English-speaking world to treat Baroque architecture as an epoch worthy of study.": [],
    "Stratton trained as an architect under Leonard A. S. Stokes (1858-1925).": [],
    "In 1895 he joined the Liverpool University College's School of Architecture as a lecturer in the practice (\"Demonstrator\").": [
